Control Mod4 F12 :TakeToWorkspace 12

# Tiling
Control Return :ToggleCmd {Maximize} {Restore}

Control Left  :ArrangeWindowsStackRight (Class!=conky)
Control Right :ArrangeWindowsStackLeft (Class!=conky)
Control Up    :ArrangeWindowsStackBottom (Class!=conky)
Control Down  :ArrangeWindowsStackTop (Class!=conky)

#RootMenu

Mod4 Mouse3 :RootMenu

